{"tid":274972,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"渾水：難估計敏華(01999.HK)誇大盈利幅度","createTime":"2017-06-07T16:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T11:36:07.000Z","uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76b5059f1ced5454cc24f8bae7d35544f85ce75e","tid":274972,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:37:29.000Z","msg":"渾水：難估計敏華(<a href=\"http://01999.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01999.HK&d=vbKq77JOvE64BzVH9oqzTU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ad19efda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01999.HK</a>)誇大盈利幅度 月內將推出另一份報告<br />\n<br />\n沽空機構渾水創辦人Carson Block表示，下一份沽空報告將於月內推出，惟對象並非港股。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，一開始關注敏華控股(<a href=\"http://01999.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01999.HK&d=vbKq77JOvE64BzVH9oqzTU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ad19efda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01999.HK</a>)  -0.670 (-10.000%)    沽空 $2.90億; 比率 34.846%   ，主要由於其盈利率大幅高於同業，其營運利潤率甚至高於蘋果公司。對於澳門相關入帳，他認為公司誇大盈利的機會高於逃稅，惟難以預測相關幅度。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，發表報告時已預計敏華會停牌。準備沽空報告期間有隱藏身份聯絡敏華員工。(vi/a)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2017-06-07 16:25。)"},{"pid":"d1ed0657657ea367a807b20643da21e82af5231d","tid":274972,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"得閒就一隻, 得閒就一隻造假<br />\n<br />\n日日出一隻呀"},{"pid":"df33afdbae757afd54e3537d54b8f718425fe0f2","tid":274972,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR，你幾時出返份呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}